data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!! Come fall in love with the 12-foot ceilings throughout entire home, spacious separate office and dining area to enjoy family gatherings over the holidays, custom shelving in laundry room, and plenty of room to put a pool in. The kitchen is any cook's dream equipped with an abundance amount of counter space, and built-in wet bar area. The owner's suite offers oversized his and her custom designed closets with not only a walk-in shower but an oversized soaking tub (BRING THE BATH BOMBS) and relax after a long day's work. The backyard is ready for its new owner to make it a true oasis.  Let us not forget this home overs a split floor plan design on an oversized corner lot offers, with over 30k in upgrades done buy seller.  Flora Parke offers LOW HOA FEES AND NO CDD FEES and is just minutes away from fine dining, shopping and the beautiful beaches of Amelia Island. Schedule your showing today!!!!
